show.description: 998 mein dobara janam leke aaya hai ek insaan jise chahiye redemption aur success. Ek galat faislon se bhari zindagi ko dubara sahi track pe lana aasaan nahi hota. Lekin Oliver ne kasam khayi hai aur is baar game paison ka nahi, izzat ka hai. Abhi dekhana shuru kijiye.
